  dialogue:
    sentences:
    - ???. Oh... you're awake. Wasn't sure you would be.
    - ???. You've been wandering for a while, haven't you? You have that look.
    - ???. Don't worry, I'm not going to keep you. Just glad to see someone come
      through.
    - ???. If you're heading further in, mind the path. Things aren't always where
      you left them.
    - "???. Take care of yourself out there. And if you can \u2014 try not to look
      back too much."
    - ???. *Press SHIFT to sprint, R to rewind time*
